data.description: Updated and move-in ready home in Tornado! Totally remodeled in 2022, this home features 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, plentiful storage throughout, and tons of finished living space on two lower levels. Open concept main floor, including living room open to dining area and kitchen with granite countertops and newer stainless steel appliances. Plentiful storage throughout! Back deck perfect for grilling overlooks the flat backyard with fire pit!
